
1. at battery connect.
	ignition on
		radio on

		radio off

	ignition off

2. vol push: toggle clock vs. current audio mode (radio, vs AU)

3. Tune push: toggle FM radio vs. Bluetooth

4. set button lites 'set' for 4-5 sec.
	radio on:
		presets stores current radio channel.
		seek&scan modify time
	radio off:
		seek&scan modify time
	bluetooth mode :
		?
		seek&scan modify time

5. seek&scann in radio mode,
	seek - seek up
	scan - seek down


